Pfizer Announces $10B Share Repurchase

-- B y   B r u c e   R u l e
-- 
2011-12-12T16:30:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/pfizer-announces-10b-share-repurchase.html
Pfizer Inc. (PFE)  said the board of
directors authorized a new share-repurchase program for as much
as $10 billion in stock.  The quarterly dividend was raised to 22 cents from 20 cents,
the New York-based company said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bruce Rule in London at 
